olong ObitFitModelDeconGau (  ofloat  bmaj,
ofloat  bmin,
ofloat  bpa,
ofloat  ebmaj,
ofloat  ebmin,
ofloat  ebpa,
ofloat  cbmaj,
ofloat  cbmin,
ofloat  cbpa,
ofloat  dgau[3][3]
) 
 

Public: Deconvolve Gaussians.

Routine translated from the AIPSish VSAD.FOR/BMVAL

Parameters:
bmaj Fitted major axis
bmin Fitted minor axis
bpa Fitted pos. angle (deg)
ebmaj Fitted major axis error
ebmin Fitted minor axis error
ebpa Fitted pos. angle error (deg)
cbmaj Clean beam major axis
cbmin Clean beam minor axis
cbpa Clean beam pos. angle (deg)
dgau Deconvolved (Major, minor, PA) array dgau[0][*] = deconvolved dgau[1][*] = upper bound dgau[2][*] = lower bound
Returns:
Error return 0-> Can completely deconvolve 1-> Cannot deconv some limits 2-> Cannot deconv fitted source
